Camera crews from the university media team are present to capture interviews. As the final hour of the fair approaches, announcement chimes resonate, and students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers. The engineering society sponsors a resume review table near the stage, and an aroma of coffee and catered snacks wafts from the lounge. Some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall.
